public abstract class TreeCellData<T> extends Object implements com.taco.tacository._to_sort.obj_traits.common.Nameable, Serializable, UIDProcessable

A wrapper class that contains an ObjectProperty containing an object of type TreeCellData to be displayed in a TreeView.

Details

  1. TreeCellData is immutable.
